      "name": "render_contract_map",
      "description": "Pure top-level function that converts per-layer type catalogues into a single-file mermaid flowchart (ADR 2026-04-17-1528 §D1). This track extends the function to generate typestate transition edges (==>) by reading TypestateTransitions::To(names) and resolving each name through type_index. Terminal typestates emit no edge; unresolved names and self-loops are silently skipped.",
